WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.300 --> 00:00:07.911
00:05
COMM: Pakkirappa Hunagundi suffers from a

00:00:07.911 --> 00:00:13.130
rare eating disorder, which makes him crave
bricks, mud and gravel.

00:00:13.130 --> 00:00:18.330
The thirty-year-old from Karnataka, India
has been consuming the unusual diet since

00:00:18.330 --> 00:00:26.029
he was ten.

00:00:26.029 --> 00:00:42.719
00:40
COMM: Hunagundi claims to consume around one

00:00:42.719 --> 00:00:46.980
brick a day, as well as eating up to two kilos
of mud and gravel.

00:00:46.980 --> 00:00:50.699
00:48
COMM: The strange habit attracts attention

00:00:50.699 --> 00:00:52.340
wherever he goes.

00:00:52.340 --> 00:01:03.249
01:02
COMM: Hunagundi 

00:01:03.249 --> 00:01:07.080
works as a labourer, but struggles to make
ends meet.

00:01:07.080 --> 00:01:12.330
He attempts to supplement his income by performing
to visitors to the village at weekends.

00:01:12.330 --> 00:01:28.830
Friends and family now want him to stop the
habit, for the good of his health.

00:01:28.830 --> 00:01:34.360
01:32
COMM: But despite the pleas of loved ones

00:01:34.360 --> 00:01:44.050
Hunagundi is adamant 
that he will continue.

00:01:44.050 --> 00:01:47.710
01:45
COMM: Hunagundi now hopes he can now turn

00:01:47.710 --> 00:02:06.130
his fame into fortune, by showcasing his ability
to eat bricks across India.

